snippet.title: SHINING NIKKI | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
------Beauty Works Miracles------
Shining Nikki presented by Papergames, the next-gen dress-up game of the Nikki series, is coming soon! 
Let's explore a world of style and infinite fashion with Nikki and Momo! 

❤️Momo has prepared some gifts for you! Go to our Facebook page for details.
■Learn more: https://www.facebook.com/ShiningNikkiGlobal/
■Official Site: https://nikki4.playpapergames.com/
